{"tid":2401720,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"15歲男生暴動及企圖縱火罪成 還押候判 期間索取勞教中心及教導所等報告","createTime":"2021-02-10T03:06:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T05:27:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"95f9243800baf32e28cc838f88ff73bfc182ccd8","tid":2401720,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:06:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13582\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13582&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=9eb64783\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13582</a><br />\n<br />\n區域法院第七庭 <br />\n#練錦鴻法官 #聆取對控罪的回答<br />\n👤* (15) #1116旺角 (原案A2)<br />\n<br />\n控罪1：暴動<br />\n被告被控於2019年11月16日，在彌敦道與山東街交界附近連同其他身份不詳人士參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n控罪4：企圖縱火<br />\n被告被控於同日在山東街與砵蘭街交界附近，將汽油彈扔到路面，企圖用火損壞路面或屬於香港特別行政區政府的財產。<br />\n<br />\n因被告承認控罪1和4，控方基於認罪協議下不會對被告起訴控罪3和5，即使被告不認罪，即「在身處非法集結時使用蒙面物品」和「管有物品意圖損壞財產」。而同案A1將會在2021年9月27日至30日面對審訊。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n基於少年犯條例3F，任何人不得透露任何人報導被告姓名、樣貌相片、或任何可令人識破其身份的資料。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n法庭把本案押後至2021年3月3日1000進行判刑。期間會為需還押的被告索取背景、勞教中心及教導所報告。"},{"pid":"b44abddd3ba68034ee349e830203c4c5a5349add","tid":2401720,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:07:31.000Z","msg":"上次提堂:<br />\n有15歲男學生及年輕地盤男工被指在旺角蒙面參與暴動，男生更被指縱火及管有一個士巴拿。兩人遭控暴動、非法集結時使用蒙面物品等罪，今日在區域法院提堂時，15歲被告透露將會認罪，代表大狀申請將被告轉介到少年庭判刑，惟因法院最快亦只能排期至明年1月中處理少年的案件，屆時少年已年屆16歲，不符少年庭處理的資格，少年最終只能維持於區域法院判刑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201215/RONYFI4ZABBUVAP44SDMPSY6EA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201215%2FRONYFI4ZABBUVAP44SDMPSY6EA%2F&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=7f2794e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201215%2FRONYFI4ZABBUVAP44SDMPSY6EA%2F&h=f1c85a8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201215/RONYFI4ZABBUVAP44SDMPSY6EA/</a>"},{"pid":"bc24ea7cd4606a7d5b5eb97588d4b41c5ad55c39","tid":2401720,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:07:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43bb1d6750a1e9ce7b845a38e45c9c7ac850aa8","tid":2401720,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:08:05.000Z","msg":"練狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deccb947f6a6110fa6271efa55d2a68af502203a","tid":2401720,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:32:04.000Z","msg":"無得更新？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d91adace784361767d55bc8e547cb403c8439fac","tid":2401720,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:32:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d23ccb44c0670b5fc0dfaaf1131612c01054b8","tid":2401720,"uid":277095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:35:48.000Z","msg":"15歲..."},{"pid":"d7df5c042418264e1a1c9ae9e893fab653ef21aa","tid":2401720,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"deccb947f6a6110fa6271efa55d2a68af502203a","tid":2401720,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:32:04.000Z","msg":"無得更新？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:36:28.000Z","msg":"無,暴動罪除非有極特殊因素先考慮"},{"pid":"6fbeb33acd678228ba0cee9a310ad8388232febf","tid":2401720,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f43bb1d6750a1e9ce7b845a38e45c9c7ac850aa8","tid":2401720,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:08:05.000Z","msg":"練狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:38:09.000Z","msg":"呢隻賤種<br />\n上左區院害死更多人"},{"pid":"9734a07f82f2d19fc88acbbc5942355ad0904112","tid":2401720,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18de96485b62d257c706d6fe87d8b2d2f4d6c73b","tid":2401720,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:26:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a94d65a5a17080ad84cbae2b9359148721b7122b","tid":2401720,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:27:26.000Z","msg":"辯方求情指被告案發時僅14歲，故《少年犯條例》在他身上適用，希望法庭考慮監禁以外的禁閉式刑罰，讓被告得以更生。律師又指，被告現時讀中四，他在運動及藝術方面成績優異，師長均讚揚他守時有禮。他今次一時衝動犯事，但就因此與父母修補關係，他們今日均有到庭支持他。被告亦自撰求情信，稱為犯事感懊悔，明白要為此付出沉重代價，承諾日後會改過自新。<br />\n<br />\n警方其後開始掃蕩，被告在便利店外投擲一枚汽油彈，汽油彈在距離警員20米外着地起火，被告隨即逃跑，惟終被截獲。被告當時戴着頭盔、防毒面具、眼鏡等，他向警方表示有人教他投擲汽油彈，而身上的扳手是用來拆除圍欄。惟他之後在父親及兄長陪同下進行錄影會面，稱扳手非他所有。"}]}